OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start to the
OL,6,Fday with occasional showers appearing
OL,7,Fthrough the morning, but these should
OL,8,Fdie away by noon, leaving a dry and
OL,9,Fincreasingly bright afternoon.
OL,10,FNortherly winds fresh across the east
OL,11,Fcoast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying dry with late
OL,14,Fsunshine then clear spells always more
OL,15,Fprolonged across southern
OL,16,FAberdeenshire. North winds
OL,17,Foccasionally fresh across the east
OL,18,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
