OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA generally fair days weather
OL,6,Fin prospect with most dry with periods
OL,7,Fof sunshine widespread through the
OL,8,Fmorning, before turning hazy from the
OL,9,Fwest during the afternoon. Winds light.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,12,Fchange to more unsettled conditions
OL,13,Fwith a series of rain bands crossing
OL,14,Ffrom the west. However, with winds
OL,15,Fstaying southwesterly temperatures a
OL,16,Flittle up on the seasonal averages.
